Released On Wednesday April 8 2026

Release Notes

1 The most notable change is that Official Triaxis Artwork Theme Is Now Archived And Official Triaxis Desktop Environment is no longer included without archive This means a official artwork theme and desktop environment is no longer available

  Official Triaxis Artwork Theme And Official Triaxis Desktop Environment had to be dropped due to lack of DIY. Of course we would appreciate  it if people would start hacking on it to bring it up to par.

2 Triaxis Switched From sudo to doas because doas is significantly lighter than sudo. Developed by the OpenBSD project
